com.koverse.sdk.transform.scala

Interface RDDTransform

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TransformDescription

    @ThreadSafe
 @Immutable
public interface RDDTransform
extends TransformDescription
    A Koverse Transform. When installed, the following methods are executed in order to obtain information on how to execute the transform: TransformDescription.getName(), TransformDescription.getVersion(), and getParameters(). These are used to provide a UI to the user to configure the transform. When the transform is executed, the execute(RDDTransformContext) method is called. It is passed a RDDTransformContext to give it the information needed to run the transform.
